Title: MHD and Cameroon football team dance like Roger Milla
Description: Warmly welcomed by the Cameroonian squad, MHD had the opportunity with PUMA Football to meet Eric-Maxim Choupo-Moting (Stoke City), Benjamin Moukandjo (Captain of the National team), Fabrice Ondoa (hero of the continent title last year), midfielder S√©bastien Siani (KV Ostende) and the Olympique de Marseille player, Frank Zambo-Anguissa. Both players and rappers lives now are closer than ever, both intertwined and obsessed with football and music respectively, bringing the culture of the game to the street and vice versa. Whether in the dance hall, the console, or the pitch this is a generation that likes to play, with style, freedom and flair. The African Football legend Roger Milla was there to witness the scenes and show his approval for the adoption and promotion of his famous hip swing and at the same time the new home kit of his Cameroon. A true handover between the old and the new generation.
